:<font size="15">צלם</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
צלם / tselem / tseh'-lem

===Etymology===
From an unused root meaning to shade; 

===Noun===
'''צלם'''

# A [[phantom]], that is, (figuratively) [[illusion]], resemblance; hence a representative figure, especially an idol: - image, vain shew.<br>An image or representation of. As in, "Man was created in the image (tselem) of God."

